name: Phishing Incident Management - Quarantine Infected Asset (FortiGate)

resource.content:
{{globalVars.Hint_Icon}} Dashboards and Reports:
  • Dashboards: To populate the Dashboards and Reports, click Execute then run the playbook: <<4 - Create Phishing Demo Records>>. Browse to Dashboards and open << Phishing Case Management >> 
  • Reports: While on the incident view, click on <<Generate Incident Summary Report>> and wait until it pops up in the comment section. You can also browse to report and explore the several built-in templates in there.
{{globalVars.Hint_Icon}} Recovery Tasks have been created automatically to remediate the infected Assets, check them out in the Tasks TAB

{{globalVars.Action_Icon}}

Navigate to Tasks

Change the Task Status to : < Completed >

 

In this Incident

  • Set the Phase to : < Aftermath >
  • Set the Status to : < Resolved >
